  <entry>
    <title>Lamdba 表达式</title>
    <url>/2019/11/12/Lambda%20%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<a id="more"></a>

<h5 id="用lambda表达式实现Runnable"><a href="#用lambda表达式实现Runnable" class="headerlink" title="用lambda表达式实现Runnable"></a>用lambda表达式实现Runnable</h5><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Java 8之前：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">new</span> Thread(<span class="keyword">new</span> Runnable() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">run</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">"Before Java8, too much code for too little to do"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;).start();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//Java 8方式：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">new</span> Thread( () -&gt; System.out.println(<span class="string">"In Java8, Lambda expression rocks !!"</span>) ).start();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="使用lambda表达式对列表进行迭代"><a href="#使用lambda表达式对列表进行迭代" class="headerlink" title="使用lambda表达式对列表进行迭代"></a>使用lambda表达式对列表进行迭代</h5><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Java 8之前：</span></span><br><span class="line">List features = Arrays.asList(<span class="string">"Lambdas"</span>, <span class="string">"Default Method"</span>, <span class="string">"Stream API"</span>, <span class="string">"Date and Time API"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (String feature : features) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(feature);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Java 8之后：</span></span><br><span class="line">List features = Arrays.asList(<span class="string">"Lambdas"</span>, <span class="string">"Default Method"</span>, <span class="string">"Stream API"</span>, <span class="string">"Date and Time API"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">features.forEach(n -&gt; System.out.println(n));</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 使用Java 8的方法引用更方便，方法引用由::双冒号操作符标示，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 看起来像C++的作用域解析运算符</span></span><br><span class="line">features.forEach(System.out::println);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">通过过滤创建一个String列表</span><br><span class="line">List&lt;String&gt; filtered = strList.stream().filter(x -&gt; x.length()&gt; <span class="number">2</span>).collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 将字符串换成大写并用逗号链接起来</span></span><br><span class="line">List&lt;String&gt; G7 = Arrays.asList(<span class="string">"USA"</span>, <span class="string">"Japan"</span>, <span class="string">"France"</span>, <span class="string">"Germany"</span>, <span class="string">"Italy"</span>, <span class="string">"U.K."</span>,<span class="string">"Canada"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">String G7Countries = G7.stream().map(x -&gt; x.toUpperCase()).collect(Collectors.joining(<span class="string">", "</span>));</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(G7Countries);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 用所有不同的数字创建一个正方形列表</span></span><br><span class="line">List&lt;Integer&gt; numbers = Arrays.asList(<span class="number">9</span>, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>);</span><br><span class="line">List&lt;Integer&gt; distinct = numbers.stream().map( i -&gt; i*i).distinct().collect(Collectors.toList());</span><br><span class="line">System.out.printf(<span class="string">"Original List : %s,  Square Without duplicates : %s %n"</span>, numbers, distinct);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//获取数字的个数、最小值、最大值、总和以及平均值</span></span><br><span class="line">List&lt;Integer&gt; primes = Arrays.asList(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">11</span>, <span class="number">13</span>, <span class="number">17</span>, <span class="number">19</span>, <span class="number">23</span>, <span class="number">29</span>);</span><br><span class="line">IntSummaryStatistics stats = primes.stream().mapToInt((x) -&gt; x).summaryStatistics();</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"Highest prime number in List : "</span> + stats.getMax());</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"Lowest prime number in List : "</span> + stats.getMin());</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"Sum of all prime numbers : "</span> + stats.getSum());</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">"Average of all prime numbers : "</span> + stats.getAverage());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Java</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Lamdba</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>跨域</title>
    <url>/2019/11/12/%E8%B7%A8%E5%9F%9F%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<a id="more"></a>

<h5 id="造成跨域的原因"><a href="#造成跨域的原因" class="headerlink" title="造成跨域的原因"></a>造成跨域的原因</h5><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">同源策略是浏览器上为安全性考虑实施的非常重要的安全策略。</span><br><span class="line">简单来说就是协议、端口、和域名有任意一个不同造成的。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="解决方法"><a href="#解决方法" class="headerlink" title="解决方法"></a>解决方法</h5><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">解决跨域问题有很多方法，可以通过浏览器，可以同前端代理，也可以后端解决。</span><br><span class="line">对于那些你调用别人的接口，你不能要求别人一定要支持跨域，这个时候只能前端解决</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h6 id="浏览器解决Chrome"><a href="#浏览器解决Chrome" class="headerlink" title="浏览器解决Chrome"></a>浏览器解决Chrome</h6><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">禁止浏览器跨域</span><br><span class="line">1.找到浏览器的安装目录，浏览器快捷键————鼠标右键————属性————目标</span><br><span class="line">2.默认安装位置C:\Program Files (x86)\Google\Chrome\Application</span><br><span class="line">3.在Application下执行打开cmd,或者打开cmd进去到Application目录下</span><br><span class="line">4.执行命令 chrome --disable-web-security</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="被调用方解决"><a href="#被调用方解决" class="headerlink" title="被调用方解决"></a>被调用方解决</h5><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Java 后台解决，实现Filter接口（基于Springboot实现的）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">@Component</span><br><span class="line">public class CorsFilter implements Filter &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    @Override</span><br><span class="line">    public void init(FilterConfig filterConfig) throws ServletException &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    @Override</span><br><span class="line">    public void doFilter(ServletRequest servletRequest, ServletResponse servletResponse, FilterChain filterChain) throws IOException, ServletException &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        HttpServletResponse response = (HttpServletResponse) servletResponse;</span><br><span class="line">        HttpServletRequest request = (HttpServletRequest) servletRequest;</span><br><span class="line">        //动态设置把*号改为request.getHeader(&quot;Origin&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">        response.setHeader(&quot;Access-Control-Allow-Origin&quot;,&quot;*&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">	//根据浏览器上面动态设置</span><br><span class="line">        response.setHeader(&quot;Access-Control-Allow-Headers&quot;, &quot;Origin, No-Cache, X-Requested-With, If-Modified-Since, Pragma, Last-Modified, Cache-Control, Expires, Content-Type, X-E4M-With, Accept, Authorization, User-Agent&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        //请求的方法</span><br><span class="line">        response.setHeader(&quot;Access-Control-Allow-Methods&quot;, &quot;HEAD, GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        //OPTIONS域检命令缓存设置过期时间</span><br><span class="line">        response.setHeader(&quot;Access-Control-Max-Age&quot;, &quot;3600&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">        filterChain.doFilter(request, response);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    @Override</span><br><span class="line">    public void destroy() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="通过nginx方法解决"><a href="#通过nginx方法解决" class="headerlink" title="通过nginx方法解决"></a>通过nginx方法解决</h5><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">server &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    listen       80;</span><br><span class="line">    server_name  localhost;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	location / &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        proxy_pass   http://ip:port/api/;</span><br><span class="line">        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Methods *;</span><br><span class="line">        add_header Access-Control-Max-Age 3600;</span><br><span class="line">        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Credentials true;</span><br><span class="line">        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin $http_origin;</span><br><span class="line">        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Headers $http_access_control_request_headers;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        if ($request_method = OPTIONS ) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            return 200;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>后续再更新</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Java</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Java</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>Linux 命令</title>
    <url>/2019/11/12/Linux%20%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<a id="more"></a>
<h5 id="系统命令"><a href="#系统命令" class="headerlink" title="系统命令"></a>系统命令</h5><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cat /etc/redhat-release 查询linux版本</span><br><span class="line">cat /proc/cpuinfo<span class="params">| grep "cpu cores"|</span> uniq  查看服务器CPU核数</span><br><span class="line">cat /proc/cpuinfo<span class="params">| grep "physical id"|</span> sort<span class="params">| uniq|</span> wc -l CPU数</span><br><span class="line">cat /proc/cpuinfo<span class="params">| grep "processor"|</span> wc -l 逻辑CPU总数</span><br><span class="line">uname -r  linux上查看系统版本</span><br><span class="line">lsof -<span class="symbol">i:</span>端口号 查看端口号使用情况</span><br><span class="line">df -T 查看分区的文件系统</span><br><span class="line">df -h 显示目前所有文件系统的可用空间及使用情形</span><br><span class="line">du -sh *   查看当前目录下各个文件及目录占用空间大小</span><br><span class="line">ls -lh  查看文件大小</span><br><span class="line">free -h      命令是一个快速查看内存使用情况的方法</span><br><span class="line">shutdown -r now 是关机后立即重新启动</span><br><span class="line">reboot  是直接重新启动</span><br><span class="line">date -R 查看时区</span><br><span class="line">env 查看所有环境变量</span><br><span class="line">vim /etc/hostname 或 hostnamectl set-hostname [NAME]  修改主机名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h5 id="进程命令"><a href="#进程命令" class="headerlink" title="进程命令"></a>进程命令</h5><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">top 显示进程   top -c 显示完整进程命令   top -p PID 显示某个PID的进程</span><br><span class="line">netstat -ano|findstr 8080</span><br><span class="line">netstat -anop | grep PID 查看指定端口的进程 </span><br><span class="line">ps -ef|grep XX 查看某个进程</span><br><span class="line">kill -9 杀掉进程</span><br><span class="line">nohup  &amp; 保护进程</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="文件命令"><a href="#文件命令" class="headerlink" title="文件命令"></a>文件命令</h5><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -ivh epel-release-<span class="number">7</span>-<span class="number">11</span>.noarch.rpm  安装rpm包命令</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>.新建一个文-件夹或文件 </span><br><span class="line">mkdir name  创建一个叫name的文件夹 </span><br><span class="line">vi test.txt 创建一个.txt文件并编辑</span><br><span class="line">touch test.sh 创建一个.txt文件</span><br><span class="line">mv test.txt tet.txt 将test.txt文件重命名为tet.txt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rpm -qa <span class="params">| grep jdk 查询所有安装的rpm包，显示名字中包含jdk的</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">yum -y remove java-1.7.0-openjdk-1.7.0.75-2.5.4.2.el7_0.x86 移除相关所有依赖的包（慎）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">clear 、CTRL+L 清屏</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">history 50 看到输入的50条命令</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">!!执行上一个命令</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">!n执行上一个n开头的命令</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">ctrl+r历史命令搜索</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">find / -name test 查看test文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">whereis    寻找特定文件，查看文件的位置只能用于搜索二进制文件(-b)、源代码文件(-s)、说明文件(-m)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">grep 'test' test*　　#显示所有以test开头的文件中包含 test的行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">tar  -zxvf   压缩文件名.tar.gz  解压tar.gz类型的文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">unzip file1.zip 解压一个zip文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">zip -r spring-boot .  压缩springboot目录到当前文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">tar -zcvf spring-boot.tar.gz spring-boot 压缩tar</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">grep  "Hello" test.txt   在test.txt文件中查找Hello,也可以在目录中查找</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">grep   -n "Hello" test/*   在test目录下所有文件中查找Hello, -n显示行数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">chown -R root：root oracle  (更改目录的权限为root)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">                在编辑某个文件的时候：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">-f 强行xx的参数。。。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">rz 上传文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">tail -f 实时监控文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">sz+文件名 下载文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">cd  进入到下一层目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">cd  -返回到上次访问目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">cd ..返回到上层目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">scp jdk-8u171-linux-x64.tar.gz  ip地址或者别名:/software </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">复制jdk到hadoop2服务器的software下（不同电脑）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">scp -r 目录/  用户名@ip:/地址   分发目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">cp -r 复制目录 （主要是同一台电脑）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">rm -rf software 删除software文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">cls 　　清屏</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">more　　分屏显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">move 　 移动文件，改目录名  move [文件名] [目录]  move [目录名] [目录名]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">exit     退出</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">net start mysql 启动mysql</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">net stop mysql  停止mysql</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">Ls -a查看列出所有文件(ll -a)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">mkdir -p 可以创建目录文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">软连接创建删除修改</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">#Linux软链接，类似于windows系统的快捷键。【目标目录】指软连接指向的目标目录下，【软链接地址】指“快捷键”文件名称</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">ln -s 【目标目录】 【软链接地址】</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">rm -rf 【软链接地址】</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">ln -snf 【新目标目录】 【软链接地址】</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h5 id="less-命令"><a href="#less-命令" class="headerlink" title="less 命令"></a>less 命令</h5><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">less 与 more 类似，但使用 less 可以随意浏览文件 </span><br><span class="line">less [参数] 文件</span><br><span class="line">-e 当文件显示结束后，自动离开</span><br><span class="line">-m 显示类似more命令的百分比</span><br><span class="line">-N 显示每行的行号</span><br><span class="line">/字符串：向下搜索<span class="string">"字符串"</span>的功能</span><br><span class="line">?字符串：向上搜索<span class="string">"字符串"</span>的功能</span><br><span class="line">b 向后翻一页</span><br><span class="line">空格键 滚动一页</span><br><span class="line">G - 移动到最后一行</span><br><span class="line">g - 移动到第一行</span><br><span class="line">F  tail -f 的效果，读取写入文件的最新内容</span><br><span class="line">Q 退出</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -h IP地址 -uroot -proot 访问别的ip上的mysql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>




<figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">开启telnet服务</span><br><span class="line">控制面板————程序和功能————打开或关闭Windows功能————找到“Telnet服务器”和“Telne客户端”两项保存</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="修改文件权限和用户组"><a href="#修改文件权限和用户组" class="headerlink" title="修改文件权限和用户组"></a>修改文件权限和用户组</h5><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">第一个字符，如果是“-”则表示是文件，如果是“d”则表示是目录</span><br><span class="line">r是<span class="number">4</span>（读），w是<span class="number">2</span>（写），x是<span class="number">1</span>（执行），-是<span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">所以上面文件是<span class="number">6</span> <span class="number">4</span> <span class="number">4</span>权限</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">修改权限命令</span><br><span class="line">chmod <span class="number">755</span> test.txt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chmod <span class="number">755</span> 文件或目录    不修改目录里面的文件</span><br><span class="line">chmod  -R <span class="number">755</span> 目录    修改目录里面的文件</span><br><span class="line">或者</span><br><span class="line">chmod +wx 文件或目录</span><br><span class="line">chmod -wx 文件或目录</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">chown 用户<span class="symbol">:</span>用户组 文件名/文件夹  <span class="comment">#修改指定文件用户</span></span><br><span class="line">chown <span class="symbol">root:</span>root test.txt</span><br><span class="line">chown -R 用户<span class="symbol">:</span>用户组 文件名/文件夹 <span class="comment">#修改文件下所有的文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="Linux-CPU问题排查"><a href="#Linux-CPU问题排查" class="headerlink" title="Linux CPU问题排查"></a>Linux CPU问题排查</h5><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>、通过top命令定位占用cpu高的进程</span><br><span class="line">top -p PID</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2</span>、通过top命令定位问题进程中每个线程占用cpu情况</span><br><span class="line">top -p PID H</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">3</span>、通过jstack 命令定位问题代码（<span class="number">142</span>ef是<span class="number">82671</span>十六进制转化成的）</span><br><span class="line">jstack PID <span class="params">| grep 142ef</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">4 Linux上转换16进制</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="params">  printf "%x\n" PID</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="Linux-用户管理"><a href="#Linux-用户管理" class="headerlink" title="Linux 用户管理"></a>Linux 用户管理</h5><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">useradd 选项 用户名<span class="symbol">:</span>添加用户账号</span><br><span class="line">userdel 选项 用户名<span class="symbol">:</span>删除用户帐号</span><br><span class="line">usermod 选项 用户名<span class="symbol">:</span>修改帐号</span><br><span class="line">passwd 用户名<span class="symbol">:</span>更改或创建用户的密码</span><br><span class="line">passwd -S 用户名 <span class="symbol">:</span>显示用户账号密码信息</span><br><span class="line">passwd -d 用户名: 清除用户密码</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">groupadd 选项 用户组 <span class="symbol">:</span>增加一个新的用户组</span><br><span class="line">groupdel 用户组<span class="symbol">:</span>要删除一个已有的用户组</span><br><span class="line">groupmod 选项 用户组 : 修改用户组的属性</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="Linux-常见参数修改"><a href="#Linux-常见参数修改" class="headerlink" title="Linux 常见参数修改"></a>Linux 常见参数修改</h5><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config</span><br><span class="line">MaxSessions：最大允许链接数，默认<span class="number">10</span>.</span><br><span class="line">MaxStartups：最大允许保持多少个未认证链接（未输入登录密码），默认值是<span class="number">10</span>.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">把他们的数字改大，例如改成</span><br><span class="line">MaxSessions <span class="number">1000</span></span><br><span class="line">MaxStartups <span class="number">1000</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">最后重启</span><br><span class="line">sshd service sshd restart</span><br><span class="line">systemctl restart sshd.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


